						in
						software develpment. I am currently seeking new opportunities and am available for hire. I am
						confident in
						my ability to bring value to any team and would love to discuss potential opportunities with
						your company.
					</p>
					<ul class="list-inline mb-0">
						<li class="list-inline-item mr-3">
							<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/faduma-ibrahim-msc-230a5387/" class="text-white">
								<i class="fab fa-linkedin fa-2x"></i>
							</a>
						</li>
						<li class="list-inline-item mr-3">
							<a href="#" class="text-white">
								<i class="fab fa-twitter fa-2x"></i>
							</a>
						</li>
						<li class="list-inline-item mr-3">
							<a href="https://github.com/fadumasaidcodes" class="text-white">
